      "text": "A rogue rainbow has exploded across Pip's garden, leaving reds crashing into oranges and purples where no purple should ever be.\n\nPip has located a bucket of paint. Starting from the top-left corner, choose a colour each turn — any region of that colour touching the flooded area joins it. Clear the whole board within the move limit!\n\nThe catch: the bucket only has so many splashes. Plan ahead — the order matters!",
